  "text": "Plasma glucose was determined in duplicate by the glucose oxidase method, using an Analox GM7 (Analox Instruments) glucose analyzer. Serum insulin was measured by immunoassay [CITATION_1] and serum free fatty acids (FFA) by fluorometric method. [CITATION_2] Glycosylated hemoglobin was measured with fast-protein liquid chromatography (MonoS, Pharmacia) and serum cholesterol and triglycerides by enzymatic methods (Hibachi 717, Automatic Analyzer, Hibachi).",
